  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the raclette-grill to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Rinse the fresh parsley and pat it dry with paper towels.",
    "Mince the garlic and red onion.",
    "Slice the red bell pepper and zucchini into thin strips.",
    "Place the clotted cream, feta cheese, paprika, salt, and black pepper in a bowl and mix until combined.",
    "Add the minced garlic and onion to the bowl and mix well.",
    "Add the sliced red bell pepper and zucchini to the bowl and mix gently to combine.",
    "Heat the raclette-grill oil in the raclette-grill and cook the mixture for 10-12 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Add the fresh mint and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a serving dish and serve hot."
  ],
